Package: mailmerge
Title: Mail Merge Using R Markdown Documents and 'gmailr`
Description: Mail merge using markdown documents and gmail. With this package
    you can parsing markdown documents as the body of email, and the `yaml` header 
    to specify the subject line of the email.  Any `{}` tags in the email will be 
    replaced with `glue`. You can preview the email in the RStudio viewer pane, and
    send (draft) email using `gmailr`.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
